entries.journal_entry_description: Rebel Agent Garek needs you to retrieve data from a terminal in Station Gamma. The data you receive should have incriminating evidence against the Empire.
entries.journal_entry_title: Gathering the Dirt on the Imperials
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Either use the Gamma Shuttle system, or fly your own space craft.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Travel to Station Gamma Via the Shuttle or Your Ship
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The Rebels think that the Empire is performing horrible experiments on Station Gamma. Go there and download information you can from the Databanks.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Retrieving Information From Station Gamma's Databanks
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Your mission for Garek is completed. Return to Tansarii space station to talk to him.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Now that you have retrieved the information from the databanks of the Station Gamma, return to Garek.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Return to Garek in the Station Master's Office
